The Big Short (2015) and the romantic musical La La Land (2016), the latter of which won him the Golden Globe Award for Best Actor and a second Academy Award nomination for Best Actor. Further acclaim followed with the science fiction thriller Blade Runner 2049 (2017) and the biopic First Man (2018). In addition to acting, he made his directorial debut in 2014\'s Lost River.','1980-11-12','None',2,NULL,'nm0331516',30614,'Acting','Ryan Gosling','London, Ontario, Canada','34.354','/lyUyVARQKhGxaxy0FbPJCQRpiaW.jpg',NULL),(730,0,'[\'Reginald Perry \', \'Билли Боб Торнтон\', \'Μπίλι Μπομπ Θόρτον\', \'빌리 밥 손튼\']','Billy Bob Thornton (born August 4, 1955) is an American actor, screenwriter, director and musician. Thornton gained early recognition as a cast member on the CBS sitcom Hearts Afire and in several early 1990s films including On Deadly Ground and Tombstone. In the mid-1990s, after writing, directing, and starring in the independent film Sling Blade, he won an Academy Award for Best Adapted Screenplay. He appeared in several major film roles following Sling Blade \'s success, including 1998\'s Armageddon and A Simple Plan. During the late 1990s, Thornton began a career as a singer-songwriter. He has released three albums and was the singer of a blues rock band.\n\nDescription above from the Wikipedia article Billy Bob Thornton, licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contributors on Wikipedia.','1955-08-04','None',2,NULL,'nm0000671',879,'Acting','Billy Bob Thornton','Hot Springs, Arkansas, USA','19.229','/uJBFml6efjg34u2jvT5ugVa1cPI.jpg',NULL),(731,0,'[\'Jessica Yu Li Henwick\', \'玉李\', \'Τζέσικα Χένγουικ\', \'제시카 헨윅\']','Jessica Yu Li Henwick (玉李) (born 30 August 1992) is an English actress. She is the first actress of East Asian descent to play the lead role in a British television series, having starred in the children\'s show Spirit Warriors. She is also known for her roles as Nymeria Sand in HBO series Game of Thrones, X-wing pilot Jessika Pava in the 2015 film