 a Primetime Emmy Award. She is a producer on the TLC reality program Who Do You Think You Are, which has garnered her five Primetime Emmy Award nominations.\n\nKudrow has also made several notable film appearances, including roles in Analyze This (1999), Dr. Dolittle 2 (2001), Bandslam (2008), Hotel for Dogs (2009), Easy A (2010), Neighbors (2014) and its sequel Neighbors 2: Sorority Rising (2016), The Girl on the Train (2016), The Boss Baby (2017), Long Shot (2019) and Booksmart (2019).\n\nDescription above from the Wikipedia article Lisa Kudrow, licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contributors on Wikipedia.','1963-07-30','None',1,NULL,'nm0001435',14406,'Acting','Lisa Kudrow','Encino, California, USA','34.632','/9YNzHuT7L0wdEl3zua6iUYz5tYT.jpg',NULL),(795,0,'[\'جيمي كيميل\', \'Τζίμι Κίμελ\', \"ג\'ימי קימל\", \'Ջեյմս Քիմել\', \'ジミー・キンメル\', \'지미 키멀\', \'ജിമ്മി കിമ്മെൽ\', \'Džimijs Kimels\', \'จิมมี คิมเมล\', \'吉米·坎摩爾\', \'James Christian Kimmel\', \'Джимми Киммел\', \'Джиммі Кіммел\']','​James Christian \"Jimmy\" Kimmel is an American comedian, actor, voice artist and television host. He is the host and creator of Jimmy Kimmel Live!, a late-night talk show that airs on ABC. Prior to that, Kimmel was best known as the co-host of Comedy Central\'s The Man Show and Win Ben Stein\'s Money. Kimmel is also a television producer, having produced shows such as Crank Yankers, Sports Show with Norm Macdonald, and The Andy Milonakis Show.','1967-11-13','None',2,NULL,'nm0453994',78303,'Acting','Jimmy Kimmel','Brooklyn, New York, USA','8.557','/wVVvvIwDtCgArdp0fsmjcM2tYyr.jpg',NULL),(796,0,'[]','Ariana Greenblatt (born 27 August 2007) is one of the busiest young actresses in Hollywood, having already been named as a \'One To Watch\' by The Hollywood Reporter on their 2019 Young Hollywood list, just a few short years into her career.','2007-08-27','None',1,NULL,'nm7567556',1767250,'Acting','Ariana Greenblatt','New York, New York, USA','29.271','/rm6yLSvxHsmyHUmKy10DmBrB4SH.jpg'