edible Burt Wonderstone (2013), and The Lazarus Effect (2015). In 2017, Wilde made her Broadway debut, playing the role of Julia in 1984. In 2019, she directed her first film, the teen comedy Booksmart, for which she won the Independent Spirit Award for Best First Feature.','1984-03-10','None',1,NULL,'nm1312575',59315,'Acting','Olivia Wilde','New York City, New York, USA','33.289','/3C7ogDK7ZrpQezMxG8ILO2ILY9a.jpg',NULL),(1480,0,'[\'KiKi Layne\', \'Kiandra Layne\']','From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia\n\nKiandra \"KiKi\" Layne (born December 10, 1991) is an American actress. She is best known for her starring roles in such films as the romantic drama If Beale Street Could Talk (2018), the drama Native Son (2019), the action superhero film The Old Guard (2020), and the romantic comedy Coming 2 America (2021).\n\nDescription above from the Wikipedia article KiKi Layne, licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contributors on Wikipedia.','1992-01-01','None',1,NULL,'nm8460487',1884703,'Acting','KiKi Layne','Cincinnati, Ohio, USA','8.167','/tDQXL6allwRzScsfxCnIlZxM4Kl.jpg',NULL),(1481,0,'[]','Kate Berlant (born July 16, 1987) is an American stand-up comedian, actress, and writer.','1987-07-16','None',1,'http://kateberlant.com/','nm2547958',1436999,'Acting','Kate Berlant','Los Angeles, California, USA','8.305','/kVUd1rIM50AsrcEmnLhaGfawNP3.jpg',NULL),(1482,0,'[\'Tim Simons\', \'Timothy C. Simons\', \'Timothy Charles Simons\']','Timothy Simons is an American film and television actor, best known for playing Jonah Ryan on the comedy television show Veep.','1978-06-12','None',2,NULL,'nm3985937',1181329,'Acting','Timothy Simons','Readfield, Maine, USA','7.305','/vG4Oob3JONf28Og8qSgbpk7M8nB.jpg',NULL),(1483,0,'[\'Zachary David Alexander Efron\', \'זאק אפרון\', \'Зак Эфрон\', \'Zachary Efron\', \'잭 에프론\', \'Zachary David Alexander \"Zac\" Efron\', \'Ζακ Έφρον\']','Zachary David Alexander Efron (born October 18, 1987) is an American actor. He began acting professionally in the e