ackson has won multiple awards throughout his career and has been portrayed in various forms of media including films, television series, and songs. In 1980, Jackson married LaTanya Richardson, with whom he has one daughter, Zoe.\n\nDescription above from the Wikipedia article Samuel L. Jackson, licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contributors on Wikipedia.','1948-12-21','None',2,NULL,'nm0000168',2231,'Acting','Samuel L. Jackson','Washington, District of Columbia, USA','54.127','/nCJJ3NVksYNxIzEHcyC1XziwPVj.jpg',NULL),(1787,0,'[\'Jacoba Francisca Maria Smulders\', \'Κόμπι Σμόλντερς\', \'寇碧·史莫德斯\', \'コビー・スマルダーズ\', \'ヤコバ・フランシスカ・マリア・スマルダーズ\']','Jacoba Francisca Maria \"Cobie\" Smulders (born April 3, 1982) is a Canadian-American actress. She is best known for her starring role as Robin Scherbatsky in the CBS sitcom How I Met Your Mother (2005–2014) and as S.H.I.E.L.D. agent Maria Hill in the Marvel Cinematic Universe superhero films The Avengers (2012), Captain America: The Winter Soldier (2014), Avengers: Age of Ultron (2015), Avengers: Infinity War (2018), Avengers: Endgame (2019), and Spider-Man: Far From Home (2019), as well as the ABC action drama series Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D (2013–2015), the Disney+ animated anthology series What If...? (2021), and the upcoming Disney+ limited series Secret Invasion (2022).\n\nSmulders\' other films include Safe Haven (2013), They Came Together (2014), Results (2015), and Jack Reacher: Never Go Back (2016). She also starred in the Netflix comedy drama series A Series of Unfortunate Events (2017), the Netflix comedy series Friends from College (2017–2019), the ABC crime drama series Stumptown (2019–2020), and the FX true crime series Impeachment: American Crime Story (2021).','1982-04-03','None',1,NULL,'nm1130627',71189,'Acting','Cobie Smulders','Vancouver, British Columbia, Canada','17.763','/eeahAe3gk050MFo3yz3FxgNp3nw.jpg',NULL),(1788,0,'[]','',NULL,'None',2,NULL,'nm1795828',1061495,'Acting','Jonathan Hansler',NULL,'1.286','/