ng from a gun toting thug to a blushing bride, a nerdy burger girl to a bratty high school drama queen.',NULL,'None',1,NULL,'nm2007472',1360385,'Acting','Myrna Velasco',NULL,'2.662','/bZ3HKdcvCSjfcAl9YWjsTDZfHIV.jpg',NULL),(2474,0,'[\'Chad Murray\', \'Chad M. Murray\', \'CMM\', \'Чад Майкл Мюррей\', \'Чад М. Мюррей\', \'Чад Мюррей\']','Chad Michael Murray (born August 24, 1981) is an American actor, writer, producer, director and former fashion model.\n\nHe is best known for playing Lucas Scott on The WB/CW drama series One Tree Hill, a recurring role as Tristan Dugray on The WB/CW series Gilmore Girls, and Charlie Todd on The WB series Dawson’s Creek. Murray had supporting roles in the films Freaky Friday, A Cinderella Story, House of Wax, and Fruitvale Station. Murray appeared in a supporting role in the Marvel/ABC series Agent Carter.','1981-08-24','None',2,'http://www.thechadmichaelmurray.com/','nm0614877',62747,'Acting','Chad Michael Murray',' Buffalo, New York, USA','24.433','/jIkzUQUVLkgn3HFMFRJBDAD0OLj.jpg',NULL),(2475,0,'[\'Джесси Меткалф\']','Jesse Eden Metcalfe (born December 9, 1978) is an American actor, most known for his role on Desperate Housewives as John Rowland. He is also notable for his portrayal of Miguel Lopez-Fitzgerald on the soap opera Passions and his starring role as the title character in the movie John Tucker Must Die.\n\nDescription above from the Wikipedia article Jesse Metcalfe, licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contributors on Wikipedia.','1978-12-09','None',2,NULL,'nm0582462',57171,'Acting','Jesse Metcalfe','Waterford, Connecticut, USA','19.256','/atp5FK0tBemYNYQfSPnI2egR7rX.jpg',NULL),(2476,0,'[]','Kelly Greyson is an actress and producer, known for Alone Yet Not Alone (2013), Little Boy (2015) and To Have and to Hold.','1991-03-12','None',1,'http://www.kellygreyson.com','nm4609675',1278867,'Acting','Kelly Greyson','Texas, USA','25.449','/dbygGZLqAqhPLQKVa24TACboAj9.jpg',NULL),(2477,0,'[\"Ser\'Darius William Blain\", \'サダリウス・ブ