ime to meet with the famed director. Zwick later informed Karl that the studio was to cast the film out of Japan, but encouraged Karl to move to Los Angeles as he saw promise in the young actor\'s talent. Inspired, Karl moved to Los Angeles, only to learn that he was offered a five year contract back in New York, on the popular daytime TV drama All My Children. Yune passed on the offer and soon booked his first lead role in the cult film Anacondas: The Hunt for the Blood Orchid. The following year Karl was picked by producer Steven Spielberg to play the memorable role of Koichi, the secret lover to Li Gong\'s Geisha Hatsumomo, in Memoirs of a Geisha, based on the international best selling novel. Karl continued to work in lead and supporting roles in award winning independent, foreign, and Hollywood films. In 2010, Karl was again chosen by producer Steven Spielberg and director Shawn Levy to star as Tak Mashido, the reclusive legend of the robot fighting world in the sci-fi drama Real Steel. Karl now resides in Los Angeles, California. His brother Rick is also a successful actor in Hollywood.','1975-04-16','None',2,NULL,'nm1400085',19860,'Acting','Karl Yune','Washington, District of Columbia, USA','3.088','/4GI4p5aPfW0vI20IdJOcxD5BEqr.jpg',NULL),(2568,0,'[]','','1999-07-17','None',1,NULL,'nm1053641',1126350,'Acting','Sophie Levy','Toronto, Canada','7.288','/ytDkZ3NrpxWayURhHuI2Dtp29TM.jpg',NULL),(2569,0,'[]','','2001-06-30','None',1,NULL,'nm8175959',2108181,'Acting','Ines Høysæter Asserson','Oslo, Norway','5.694','/fs2Kgd4RpfiWxHXulX1wnRAknjq.jpg',NULL),(2570,0,'[\'Veslemøy Evenstad Mørkrid\']','',NULL,'None',1,'https://www.morkrid.com/','nm3943964',1349664,'Acting','Veslemøy Mørkrid',NULL,'3.196','/kRp7lr5GRipPU8qb5Cg32zjoIW0.jpg',NULL),(2571,0,'[\' Elli Rhiannon Müller\', \'Elli Rhiannon Müller Osbourne\']','Elli Rhiannon Müller Osborne is a Norwegian actress, known for Utøya: July 22 (2018), Hope (2019), Vikingulven (2022), and the Netflix movie Royalteen (2022).