and leading roles in The Beguiled (2017), and the black comedy series On Becoming a God in Central Florida (2019), for which she received a third Golden Globe nomination. She earned nominations for her fourth Golden Globe and first Academy Award nomination for her performance in the psychological drama The Power of the Dog (2021).','1982-04-30','None',1,NULL,'nm0000379',205,'Acting','Kirsten Dunst','Point Pleasant, New Jersey, USA','24.642','/sFYHUU1gWd57pttD8732tkBsXV5.jpg',NULL),(3140,0,'[\'Джим Парсонс\', \'Джеймс Джозеф Парсонс\', \'짐 파슨스\', \'Τζιμ Πάρσονς\', \'جيم بارسنز\', \'جِم بارسِنْز\']','Jim Parsons is an American television and film actor, best known for playing Sheldon Cooper in The Big Bang Theory.','1973-03-24','None',2,NULL,'nm1433588',5374,'Acting','Jim Parsons','Houston, Texas, USA','23.801','/sa05slVgacuXe94UFnQs4rfqZL4.jpg',NULL),(3141,0,'[\'Mahershalalhashbaz Ali\', \'Mahershala Karim-Ali \', \'마허샬라 알리\', \'Махершала Али\', \'Hershal Gilmore\', \'Mahershalalhashbaz Gilmore\']','Mahershalalhashbaz \"Mahershala\" Ali (born Mahershalalhashbaz Gilmore; February 16, 1974) is an American actor. Ali began his career as a regular on series such as Crossing Jordan and Threat Matrix before his breakthrough role as Richard Tyler in the science-fiction series The 4400. His first major film release was in the 2008 David Fincher-directed romantic fantasy drama film The Curious Case of Benjamin Button. His other notable films include Predators and The Place Beyond the Pines. He played a major role in Free State of Jones, set during and after the American Civil War.\n\nAli is best known for his recent roles as Remy Danton in House of Cards, Cornell \"Cottonmouth\" Stokes in Netflix\'s TV series Luke Cage, Juan in Moonlight, and Boggs in The Hunger Games: Mockingjay – Part 1 and its sequel, The Hunger Games: Mockingjay – Part 2.','1974-02-16','None',2,NULL,'nm0991810',932967,'Acting','Mahershala Ali','Oakland, California, USA','15.019','/9ZmSejm5lnUVY5IJ1iNx2QEj