 Actors Guild Award.\n\nAniston has been included in numerous magazines\' lists of the world\'s most beautiful women. She is the recipient of a star on the Hollywood Walk of Fame and is the co-founder of the production company Echo Films, established in 2008.','1969-02-11','None',1,NULL,'nm0000098',4491,'Acting','Jennifer Aniston','Sherman Oaks, Los Angeles, California, USA','23.771','/o5jCZTBv49mh2JhIpsw3FkGuns7.jpg',NULL),(4656,0,'[\'Бруклин Декер\']','Brooklyn Decker is an American film and television actress and former model.','1987-04-12','None',1,NULL,'nm2395937',131520,'Acting','Brooklyn Decker','Kettering, Ohio, USA','9.542','/x3JWepaXTopE9k0g87Q9diRM5Nc.jpg',NULL),(4657,0,'[\'Vanessa Nicole Villalovos\']','','1977-09-16','None',1,NULL,'nm1699630',2686992,'Acting','Vanessa Villalovos','Mission Viejo, California, USA','2.509','/5XH1y9wB71y6gZi06iJSCnwvqVQ.jpg',NULL),(4658,0,'[]','Griffin Gluck (born August 24, 2000) is an American actor. In television, he is known for his roles as Charlie in Red Band Society, Mason Warner in Private Practice, and Danny Gannon in Back in the Game. He also starred as a main character in the Hulu movie Big Time Adolescence. He acted as Sam Ecklund in both seasons of the Netflix mockumentary series American Vandal and played Gabe in the Netflix series Locke & Key. In film, he portrayed Rafe Khatchadorian in the film Middle School: The Worst Years of My Life and Jack Dunkleman in the Netflix original movie Tall Girl.','2000-08-24','None',2,NULL,'nm3838034',971299,'Acting','Griffin Gluck','Los Angeles, California, USA','11.802','/j7KSBKYLgnLxkZfhQ679HRSDIjj.jpg',NULL),(4659,0,'[\'Hammer & Tongs\']','Garth Jennings is an English film director, screenwriter, producer, actor and writer. Films he has directed include The Hitchhiker\'s Guide to the Galaxy, Son of Rambow, and Sing. He co-founded the production company Hammer & Tongs.  Description above from the Wikipedia article Hammer & Tongs, licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contr