nded Ramakrishna Mission Ashram, Baranagar Mission and later did his high school from Hindu School. He perused his graduation in Political Science Honours from Jadavpur University.\n\nAfter completion of high school he joined the theatre group as trainer. He was part of T.I.E. Project (Theater in Education), under the guidance of Rudra Prasad Sengupta. He also attended workshop conducted by Ibrahim Alkazi. During his acting days he was also working as a freelance journalist in \'Anandalok\' (a film Magazine of A.B.P. Group), guided by Rituporno Ghosh. He started acting in television serials like Ekushe Pa, Ghoom Nei, Janmabhoomi etc. He got his first acting career break in the year 1995 in the serial \"Ekushe Pa\" directed by Raja Dasgupta for Zee Bangla.\n\nHe has been associated with ETV Bangla - a 24-hrs regional satellite channel of Eenadu Group right from its inception where he is responsible for conceptualizing, designing &amp; producing 6 hours of original programming daily. He was a senior programming associate at ETV Bangla (1999 to 2002). He has designed more than 50 non-fiction shows for Bengali television. He conceptualised the first Bengali women\'s magazine programmes on television - \'Sreemoti\'. He launched the first reality show format in Bengali television - Ritur Mela Jhoom Tara Ra Ra as a director and producer he has worked with all leading channels in West Bengal and Bangladesh. He has designed more than 10,000 hours of television programme.\n\nHe started his own company named \'Windows Productions\' along with his partner Nandita Roy. Together they produced many non-fiction and fiction programmes.',NULL,'None',0,NULL,'nm1425585',1417485,'Directing','Shiboprosad Mukherjee','Kolkata, West Bengal, India','1.747','/5ZwTd4jcadjqS6p2NI9TjNea89x.jpg',NULL),(5719,0,'[\'Gargi Raychowdhury\', \'Gargi Roychowdhury\', \'Gargi Roy Chowdhury\', \'Gargee Roy Chowdhury\']','Gargee RoyChowdhury is an Indian Bengali actress. She works in Bengali movies in Kolkata and soaps in television. RoyChowdhury is one of the most popular actresses of the Bengali screen. An outstanding actress, Gargee began her career as a theatre artiste, performing in Uttaran and later Bohurupee. She has also been a newscaster and radio artist. She is also an anchor. In television and films she has portrayed a variety of characters. RoyChowdhury has been hailed as the Undisputable Reigning Queen of \"tellywood\" for more than a decade. Her next film is Mahananda.','1975-04-23','None',1,NULL,'nm3437910',1391774,'Acting','Gargee RoyChowdhury','Kolkata, West Bengal, India','2.343','/zJtleRphRTspWtfj2F6yqKiAlka.jpg',NULL),(5720,0,'[]','',NULL,'None',0,NULL,NULL,2072880,'Acting','Broto Banerjee',NULL,'1.394',NULL,NULL),(5721,0,'[\'Sunjay Dutt\', \'Shri Sanjay Dutt\', \'संजय दत्त\', \'Master Sanjay Dutt\', \'Baba\', \'Санджай Датт\']','Sanjay Dutt (born 29 July 1959) is an Indian Hindi film actor and politician. Dutt is the son of Hindi film stars Sunil and Nargis Dutt. He made his debut in 1981.\n\nDescription above from the Wikipedia article Sanjay Dutt, licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contributors on Wikipedia.','1959-07-29','None',2,NULL,'nm0004569',85881,'Acting','Sanjay Dutt','Mumbai, Maharashtra, India','3.127','/zhYAdzlDMbhWr8ZBVDK02nrwnOJ.jpg',NULL),(5722,0,'[\'Chandra Shekhar\', \'Bhaiya\']','Chandra Shekhar known by his stage name Raaj Vishwakarma, Raaj Vishwakarma is an youngest Indian actor and social media influencer. His official birth date is 01 july 1995 and actual birth date is 28 March 1995. Raaj made his Bollywood debut in 2017, with a small role in Taapsee Pannu starrer, Running Shaadi. Later he apprared in few other small roles. Few of his movies are Gangubai Kathiawadi, Tadap, Decoupled (Series), Aranyak (Series), No means no etc. He did his graduation at University of Kanpur, Uttar Pradesh. He had a hobby of acting from his childhood. His father name is Awadhesh Kumar and mother name is Usha Devi.','1995-03-28','None',2,NULL,